api_list.name: /parseUrl
api_list.description: Parse a Realtor.ca search URL to extract search query and filters.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://realtor-ca-scraper-api.p.rapidapi.com/parseUrl"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "realtor-ca-scraper-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
